      "text": "演唱：六哲",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 21.53,
      "time_str": "00:21.530",
      "text": "下着雨的天气",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 25.12,
      "time_str": "00:25.120",
      "text": "好象你可爱的坏脾气",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 29.38,
      "time_str": "00:29.380",
      "text": "我的爱 我的心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 33.19,
      "time_str": "00:33.190",
      "text": "早就已经交给了你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 37.29,
      "time_str": "00:37.290",
      "text": "你说我 很不错",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 40.65,
      "time_str": "00:40.650",
      "text": "是不是在暗示什么",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.66,
      "time_str": "00:44.660",
      "text": "可不可以 坦白地说",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.33,
      "time_str": "00:48.330",
      "text": "不要再让我受折磨",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 51.68,
      "time_str": "00:51.680",
      "text": "想起我们的点点滴滴",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 55.87,
      "time_str": "00:55.870",
      "text": "我们也有美好回忆",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 59.75,
      "time_str": "00:59.750",
      "text": "我的记忆里 全部是你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 63.26,
      "time_str": "01:03.260",
      "text": "叫我如何不想你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
